🎉 Day 100 – Road to Fluent Spanish Summary 🇪🇸
Today marks a major milestone: 100 consecutive days of studying Spanish. Over the past 100 days, you have consistently completed Duolingo, Memrise, Pimsleur, handwritten notes, conversation practice, real-world speaking, and daily review. Today’s session focused on beginning a new week of conversational phrases while starting Pimsleur Unit 3, Lesson 12.

